OL,3,CRates hikes across Northern Ireland
OL,5,FHousehold rates bills are made up of
OL,6,Ftwo components. The district rate, set
OL,7,Fby councils and the regional rate,
OL,8,Fdecided by Stormont.
OL,10,FRegional rates pay for education,
OL,11,Femergency services, hospitals,
OL,12,Fjustice, social services and community
OL,13,Fdevelopment.
OL,15,FExecutive members have said they are
OL,16,Fkeen to avoid a sharp rise in regional
OL,17,Frates amid pressure from the Treasury
OL,18,Fto raise #113 million in revenue
OL,19,Fwithin the next budget.
