OL,3,CRates hikes across Northern Ireland
OL,5,FThe UK Government has offered to wipe
OL,6,F#600million of Stormont debt
OL,7,Fconditional on the Executive raising
OL,8,F#113 million, the equivalent of a 15
OL,9,Fpercent regional rate increase.
OL,11,FFirst Minister Michelle O'Neill has
OL,12,F"ruled out" a 15 percent regional
OL,13,Frates increase.
OL,15,FThe figure will be decided by the
OL,16,FExecutive in the coming weeks.
OL,18,FDistrict rates support the arts,
OL,19,Fbuilding control, leisure, community
OL,20,Finitiatives, environmental health,
OL,21,Ftourism and waste management.
